  "description": "<b>市民轻信小区内、街边的低价“山寨宽带”小广告，安装后不久就开始出现断网、卡机、甚至无法下载等多方面问题，当联系当初巧舌如簧的推销商家，却发现售后维权问题无法得到保障！</b>这样的情况屡见不鲜，“山寨宽带”打着低价销售的旗号弄虚作假，服务缺斤短两。究其原因，在市场相关监管缺失的背景下，贪小便宜吃大亏。消费者应当擦亮双眼选择正规渠道办理业务，相关部门也应该加快脚步出台相关监管政策与法律法规，多方联动形成合力规范宽带市场。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d7cbd36/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241733.htm&amp;t=%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%9C%B0%E6%91%8A%E4%BB%B7%E8%97%8F%E7%8C%AB%E8%85%BB+%E5%81%87%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%91%BC%E5%94%A4%E7%9B%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241733.htm&amp;t=%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%9C%B0%E6%91%8A%E4%BB%B7%E8%97%8F%E7%8C%AB%E8%85%BB+%E5%81%87%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%91%BC%E5%94%A4%E7%9B%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241733.htm&amp;t=%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%9C%B0%E6%91%8A%E4%BB%B7%E8%97%8F%E7%8C%AB%E8%85%BB+%E5%81%87%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%91%BC%E5%94%A4%E7%9B%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241733.htm&amp;t=%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%9C%B0%E6%91%8A%E4%BB%B7%E8%97%8F%E7%8C%AB%E8%85%BB+%E5%81%87%E5%AE%BD%E5%B8%A6%E5%91%BC%E5%94%A4%E7%9B%91%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\